{"tid":1612393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港8月零售總銷貨值大跌23% (市場預期跌14%)","createTime":"2019-10-02T08:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T10:10:44.000Z","uid":70194,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a64848eb1024d51ee795095da5f911e00743cfe4","tid":1612393,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"政府統計處公布，香港今年8月零售業總銷貨價值的臨時估計為294億港元，<span style=\"color: red;\">按年下跌23%，為連跌7個月，市場預期跌14%。</span><br />\n政府發言人表示，零售業銷售在8月進一步明顯轉差，錄得有紀錄以來最大的單月按年跌幅，較亞洲金融風暴期間在1998年9月錄得的跌幅更差。8月份零售業銷售急跌除了由於經濟狀況欠佳令消費情緒疲弱外，亦主要反映本地社會事件對訪港旅遊業及與消費相關的活動構成的嚴重干擾。<br />\n<br />\nif you burn, you burn with us.jpg"},{"pid":"88f91fddcc00bc1100834090b4b9df10636982c4","tid":1612393,"uid":70194,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:45:51.000Z","msg":"edit: if we burn, you burn with us!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfc83ce6cdc09d14b3264b2b1e3f70d2b9be749","tid":1612393,"uid":22047,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"屌，我仲以為直線插水到零，23%喳嘛，得，大家要加把勁"},{"pid":"c93f53d7cbf7c2354ee9e57145ebde9c45da73f0","tid":1612393,"uid":70194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f66e6002d44fca1bb2c7b602ffaf9c2c93da2253","tid":1612393,"uid":12166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:47:19.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"e6afd4b163324f2d12f85fe6378b5541dcc7231f","tid":1612393,"uid":70194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8cfc83ce6cdc09d14b3264b2b1e3f70d2b9be749","tid":1612393,"uid":22047,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"屌，我仲以為直線插水到零，23%喳嘛，得，大家要加把勁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"都仲未計埋9月<img src=\"/asse